Blog post detailing a flaw in my CM9:  http://www.thebangswitch.com/flaw-in-the-kahr-cm9/

The Kahr CM9 9mm pocket pistol is a small, light weight, reliable handgun that features a polymer frame. The Kahr CM9 is a lower cost alternative to the Kahr PM9 9mm pistol. The Kahr CM9 competes against the Ruger LC9 and Kel-Tec PF-9 both price wise and size wise.

